You can see a fallen tree, an apple and Your Dog.

You can go north, south or east.

You are in the Southern Meadow, on the edge of the Northern Woods

> x tree

> x tree

It's a fallen poplar tree, looks like it got too top heavy and was ripped down by the wind
> x apple

> x apple

A medium sized apple of the Cox's variety, it is mottled green and red.
> take it

> take it

You pick it up.
> chop tree

> chop tree

You swing your trusty axe and reduce the tree to four body-length logs

> x logs

> x logs

Four body-length sized logs from a poplar tree
