No Win
> play bandit

> play bandit

There is one credit left on the machine. You pull the arm on the machine for the final play, the reels whirl and spin...

The first reel clonks to stop = Skull....
....The second reel clonks to a stop = Skull...
...The third reel clonks to a stop = Skull !

There is a satisfying Ker-Chunk, Ker-Chunk, Ker-Chunk noise and three coins are deposited in the tray. You place them in your pocket.

The Landlord walks across to the machine. Muttering under his breath he locks it shut and places an 'Out of Order' sign across it.

Suddenly the doors of the pub fly open and in comes one very tall guy and one very short, huffing and puffing as they manoeuvre a piano into the pub.

"Here you go Jack" the short guys shouts, "Will settle up with you in the week", and they both leave.
