You are in Prison Cell 37927.

You can see The  and .

You slowly come round and realise you are in a dark and dank prison cell, it stinks in here.

Dylan is pawing at your chest, you sit up, with your head still spinning you hear a voice you've not heard in years, "Hello my child" says the Bony King. "Hello Dad", you reply.

